29 operation, technology needs, or improvement of the office.
30 Section 3. The collection and expenditure of fees for
31 remote access of records in the office of the judge of probate
32 by computer or other electronic or digital system prior to the
33 effective date of this act are ratified and confirmed.
34 Section 4. This act shall become effective on June 1,
35 2026.
